From 1cb8f357753fd6d76fd130fd4af683467c8e45c6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: LiangCheng Wang <zaq14760@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 17:52:10 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2/5] plat: renesas: rzv2h: add BL22 loading support for CM33

Add the platform image description, memory range and
storage policies needed to load the Cortex-M33 firmware as BL22.

When CM33 firmware loading is enabled, BL2 can fetch the BL22 image from
the selected boot device and map the BL22 SRAM region.
Skip loading BL22 during warm boot.
---
 plat/renesas/rz/common/v2h_common.mk          | 14 +++
 .../rz/soc/v2h/bl2_plat_mem_params_desc.c     | 94 +++++++++++++++++++
 plat/renesas/rz/soc/v2h/bl2_plat_setup.c      | 15 +++
 .../rz/soc/v2h/include/plat_tbbr_img_def.h    |  7 +-
 .../renesas/rz/soc/v2h/include/platform_def.h |  8 ++
 plat/renesas/rz/soc/v2h/include/rz_soc_def.h  | 11 +++
 plat/renesas/rz/soc/v2h/plat_storage.c        | 40 +++++++-
 plat/renesas/rz/soc/v2h/platform.mk           |  8 ++
 8 files changed, 194 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 plat/renesas/rz/soc/v2h/bl2_plat_mem_params_desc.c

diff --git a/plat/renesas/rz/common/v2h_common.mk b/plat/renesas/rz/common/v2h_common.mk
